imdb.plot outline: An Unusual Behind The Scenes Look at the making of the feature film "Lost And Found In Armenia." This is a web-series of the day-to-day life On Set while making a movie. From the POV of a film crew member the public gets to see up close what one's person experience was during the 30 days of filming a feature film in a foreign country, Armenia.
imdb.title: Movie Set Life
